Conclusion The FAIR Data Point Populator addresses several limitations of other tools. It makes creating metadata easier, ensures adherence to a common metadata schema, allows bulk creation of metadata entries and increases collaboration. As a result of this, the barrier of entry for FAIRification is lower, which enables the creation of FAIR data by more people.},
